{"tid":1843140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"13:00 旺角突發！一手料！即將大量支那毒人以Passport入境！","createTime":"2020-01-26T05:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T12:57:50.000Z","uid":141489,"like":162,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"eee7311f59b6a1c34ebafc9b4c881d686e43fb1a","tid":1843140,"uid":141489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"13:00 旺角突發！一手料！即將大量支那毒人以Passport入境！<br />\n<br />\n啱啱旺角一手，喺茶記聽到相入面條撚樣講電話，<br />\n大大聲安排支那人經深圳落香港，<br />\n全部用Passport，集團式經營，<br />\n條友廣東話有口音，有時又講支那語，<br />\n電話講緊嗰批聽日下畫三點會到港，<br />\n有提過黃崗，可能一路都做緊，<br />\n海關小心下晏三點，帶好裝備，唔好瀨嘢害埋屋企人<br />\n有提過先帶一批，其他再搞，可能想用其他方法暗地入境！<br />\n<br />\n盡快推到上傳媒！要求全面開花抗毒！<br />\n要逼林奠條八婆封關！！<br />\n咪撚再毒害香港！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4a1EDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4a1EDU.jpg&h=76539c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBCCXqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBCCXqA.jpg&h=23152e67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vG4CqB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vG4CqB.jpg&h=6f8a6431&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d14c1038785a74a3964eb927ec7ebd3f07e887d","tid":1843140,"uid":36673,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"推到海關手足知"},{"pid":"8d2290bcf2b077db265db152eb0caf9c402f5131","tid":1843140,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推到入境手足知</blockquote>"},{"pid":"985905f0133c18ca00edf693be40c27de1310da7","tid":1843140,"uid":25367,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"空ac看圖說故事？"},{"pid":"9fc38074efac3e8c801f92a3842f9ece8eed7ad4","tid":1843140,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"仲係關口番工果d小心 咪累埋屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f